{"tid":1108012,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"港5大學在日內瓦國際發明展奪得獎項","createTime":"2019-04-15T15:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T01:37:13.000Z","uid":138707,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2493648031728467519e4467bf46f8df36edef4","tid":1108012,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"本港5間大學及7間科研機構，共近120個的發明項目參展，共獲得56個金獎及53個銀獎。<br />\n其中理工大學、中文大學及浸會大學的發明，獲得一共35個獎項，三間大學的得獎項目範疇，涵蓋人工智能、智慧燈柱、醫療等方面。<br />\n<br />\n港大奪五金五銀 <br />\n<br />\n城大奪兩金兩銀<br />\n<br />\n中大獲14獎 建人工智慧燈柱 推動智慧城市，包括2個評判嘉許特別金獎、1個金獎、8個銀獎、2個銅獎及羅馬尼亞創新科技協會特別大獎。<br />\n<br />\n理大獲得18個獎項，包括4項特別大獎、2項評判特別嘉許金獎、3項金獎、2項銀獎，以及7項優異獎。<br />\n<br />\n浸大獲3獎，奪得一項評判嘉許特別金獎、一項金獎和一項銀獎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實點解科大冇份？明明科大研究應該係全港咁多大學當中最勁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934d01b14349fa0e7bdcf9196cadb86a3685a9c0","tid":1108012,"uid":59848,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:54:53.000Z","msg":"無參加咪無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118bf84d024f7245f53805e764cae329b43459bf","tid":1108012,"uid":201890,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"其實科大唔稀罕d 雞毛蒜皮既獎項。"},{"pid":"04d6b009bddc0a0cbcc248319fb0a974fa4ec1d0","tid":1108012,"uid":152520,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"港5大學參展，5大學奪得獎項，tvb豬肉奬？😂"},{"pid":"d6ea224a71b2fea9ef2e361244f8bf8318a886f7","tid":1108012,"uid":236414,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"點解禾含冇份？明明一大"},{"pid":"76ed04b021fe68b3924ac689f3b6f264d173eeaf","tid":1108012,"uid":138707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d6ea224a71b2fea9ef2e361244f8bf8318a886f7","tid":1108012,"uid":236414,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"ci